flex2.compiler.config

Class ServicesDependenciesWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • flex2.compiler.config.ServicesDependenciesWrapper

  • public class ServicesDependenciesWrapper
extends Object
    Flex MXMLC compiler uses the result of the client configuration parser to generate mixin initialization source code to be added to the SWF by PreLink. It also requires a list of channel classes to be added as dependencies.
